<p>Brooklyn and Lottie have been pals for a number of years and it is claimed that she made it clear their liaison wasn't a serious thing. </p>

<p>The alleged fling was said to be 'embarrassing' for the Beckham family, as both Brooklyn and his parents have socialised with Lottie's supermodel sister Kate in the past.</p>

<p>After connecting with Brooklyn, the model is said to have become pals with now ex-girlfriend Hana, who split with the photographer over the summer.  </p>

